data.name: label105.Text
data.value: Resin, which has a lower Dk (Dkr~3) and higher Df (Dfr~0.022) than e-glass, will fill the gaps between traces. Initial values come from program settings. Consult your laminate manufacturer for actual resin Dk and Df.

data.value: Laminate-side roughness (Rz) is controlled by the laminate manufacturer. Prepreg-side roughness (Rz) is determined by the oxide treatment used by the PCB manufacturer. (Range: 0.5 - 15 um)
